  <intervention>
    <intervention_type>Behavioral</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>Adherence report</intervention_name>
    <description>During the intervention phase, the data collected at the study visit were summarized in a 3-page report that was given to the provider before each intervention visit. The report included data on self-reported adherence, MEMS adherence, reminder use, beliefs about ART, reasons for missed doses, alcohol and drug use, and depression.</description>
